{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882609495,"sessionID":"ses_28528da7fffeeEo22z8KG7QLjm","part":{"id":"prt_d7ada2009001bsfP4kyQVrKFh0","messageID":"msg_d7ada08d3001Xt4bVIGqztIruY","sessionID":"ses_28528da7fffeeEo22z8KG7QLjm","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_e396dc9475eb4aaeae541a7f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Delta Spec\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** L\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Overview\n10: \n11: This delta-spec defines specific test scenarios to be implemented for the router, store, and picod modules.\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Test Scenarios\n16: \n17: ### router 模块\n18: \n19: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n20: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n21: | AR-039-001-A | router | TBD | TBD | 🔲 |\n22: | AR-039-001-B | router | TBD | TBD | 🔲 |\n23: \n24: ### store 模块\n25: \n26: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n27: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n28: | AR-039-002-A | store | TBD | TBD | 🔲 |\n29: | AR-039-002-B | store | TBD | TBD | 🔲 |\n30: \n31: ### picod 模块\n32: \n33: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n34: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n35: | AR-039-003-A | picod | TBD | TBD | 🔲 |\n36: | AR-039-003-B | picod | TBD | TBD | 🔲 |\n37: \n38: ---\n39: \n40: ## Dependencies\n41: \n42: - Go 1.21+\n43: - `testing` package (stdlib)\n44: - Additional testing utilities as needed\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ## Notes\n49: \n50: - This delta-spec will be populated with detailed test scenarios after code analysis\n51: - Each scenario should be independently verifiable\n52: - Use table-driven test patterns where appropriate\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Delta Spec\n\n> **Module:** pkg\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines specific test scenarios to be implemented for the router, store, and picod modules.\n\n---\n\n## Test Scenarios\n\n### router 模块\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775882609485,"end":1775882609493}}}}
