{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775882611429,"sessionID":"ses_28528da7fffeeEo22z8KG7QLjm","part":{"id":"prt_d7ada2ae2001NT94NldYkg57b5","messageID":"msg_d7ada2390001tttreqdNYQJKec","sessionID":"ses_28528da7fffeeEo22z8KG7QLjm","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882661409,"sessionID":"ses_28528da7fffeeEo22z8KG7QLjm","part":{"id":"prt_d7ada2e40001ufG96lEq0MZQHa","messageID":"msg_d7ada2390001tttreqdNYQJKec","sessionID":"ses_28528da7fffeeEo22z8KG7QLjm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_8dc4c48075fa4c29b0a01492","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Delta Spec\n\n> **Module:** pkg\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Go unit tests for three core modules:\n- **pkg/router**: HTTP routing, proxy, health checking, rate limiting, authentication, session management, JWT\n- **pkg/store**: Valkey/Redis-backed session and sandbox storage\n- **pkg/picod**: Pico execution server with command execution and file handling\n\n---\n\n## Test Scenarios\n\n### router 模块 - 初始化和配置\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-001-A | router | NewRouter | Router creates with default config when nil is passed | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-001-B | router | NewRouter | Router creates with custom config with SessionEnabled and JWTEnabled | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-001-C | router | AddBackend/RemoveBackend | Router adds and removes backends | 🔲 |\n\n### router 模块 - Backend Pool 和健康检查\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-002-A | router | GetBackendForRequest | Backend pool routes requests to matching prefix | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-002-B | router | HealthChecker.Start/Stop | Health checker monitors backends and marks unavailable | 🔲 |\n\n### router 模块 - 限流\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-003-A | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter allows requests under limit | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-003-B | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter blocks requests over limit with 429 | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-003-C | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter can be disabled | 🔲 |\n\n### router 模块 - 认证\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-004-A | router | Authenticator.Middleware | Authenticator validates token correctly | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-004-B | router | Authenticator.Middleware | Authenticator can be disabled | 🔲 |\n\n### router 模块 - Session 管理\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-005-A | router | SessionManager | Session manager creates session | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-005-B | router | SessionManager | Session cleanup removes expired sessions | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-005-C | router | SessionMiddleware | Session middleware attaches session to request | 🔲 |\n\n### router 模块 - JWT 认证\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-006-A | router | JWTManager.GenerateToken | JWT manager creates token with correct claims | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-006-B | router | JWTManager.ValidateToken | JWT manager validates valid/expired/invalid tokens | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-006-C | router | JWTMiddleware.Middleware | JWT middleware enforces authentication | 🔲 |\n\n### router 模块 - 日志和指标\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-007-A | router | Logger.Middleware | Logger records request details | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-007-B | router | Metrics | Metrics records request stats correctly | 🔲 |\n\n### store 模块 - Store 接口\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-008-A | store | Store interface | Store implements complete Store interface | 🔲 |\n\n### store 模块 - Valkey Store\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-009-A | store | newValkeyStore | Valkey store connects with credentials | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-B | store | newValkeyStore | Valkey store requires VALKEY_ADDR | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-C | store | StoreSandbox | Valkey store stores sandbox with indices | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-D | store | GetSandboxBySessionID | Valkey store retrieves sandbox | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-E | store | GetSandboxBySessionID | Valkey store returns ErrNotFound for non-existent session | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-F | store | UpdateSandbox | Valkey store updates sandbox | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-G | store | DeleteSandboxBySessionID | Valkey store deletes sandbox and indices | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-H | store | ListExpiredSandboxes | Valkey store lists expired sandboxes | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-I | store | ListInactiveSandboxes | Valkey store lists inactive sandboxes | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-J | store | StoreSandbox | Valkey store validates input (nil, zero expiry, empty sessionID) | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-K | store | UpdateSessionLastActivity | Valkey store updates last activity | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-009-L | store | Close | Valkey store closes connection | 🔲 |\n\n### picod 模块 - Server 初始化\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-010-A | picod | NewServer | Server creates with valid config | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-010-B | picod | NewServer | Server validates config | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-010-C | picod | setWorkspace | Server sets workspace directory | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-010-D | picod | setWorkspace | Server uses cwd when workspace is empty | 🔲 |\n\n### picod 模块 - 路径安全\n\n| ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n|----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n| AR-039-011-A | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization allows safe paths | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-011-B | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization blocks escape attempts | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-011-C | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization blocks absolute paths | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-011-D | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization handles sy