picod | LoadRSAPublicKey | LoadRSAPublicKey parses valid PEM | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-015-C | picod | LoadRSAPublicKey | LoadRSAPublicKey rejects invalid PEM | 🔲 |\n| AR-039-015-D | picod | LoadRSAPublicKey | LoadRSAPublicKey rejects non-RSA key | 🔲 |\n\n---\n\n## 测试文件状态\n\n### router 模块\n\n| Source File | Test File | Status |\n|-------------|-----------|--------|\n| server.go | server_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n| config.go | config_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| route.go | route_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| backend.go | backend_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| health.go | health_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| ratelimit.go | ratelimit_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| auth.go | auth_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| session.go | session_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| jwt.go | jwt_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| logging.go | logging_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| metrics.go | (使用已有) | N/A |\n\n### store 模块\n\n| Source File | Test File | Status |\n|-------------|-----------|--------|\n| store.go | (仅接口) | N/A |\n| store_valkey.go | store_valkey_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n| store_redis.go | store_redis_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n\n### picod 模块\n\n| Source File | Test File | Status |\n|-------------|-----------|--------|\n| server.go | server_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n| execute.go | execute_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n| auth.go | auth_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n| files.go | files_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n| health.go | health_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n\n---\n\n## 验收标准\n\n- [ ] AC001: Router Config 初始化和默认值测试\n- [ ] AC002: Router 创建各种配置组合测试\n- [ ] AC003: BackendPool AddBackend, RemoveBackend, GetBackendForRequest 测试\n- [ ] AC004: HealthChecker Start, Stop, checkBackend 测试\n- [ ] AC005: RateLimiter Allow, Middleware 测试\n- [ ] AC006: Authenticator Middleware 启用/禁用状态测试\n- [ ] AC007: SessionManager Create, Get, Delete, Cleanup 测试\n- [ ] AC008: JWTManager GenerateToken, ValidateToken 测试\n- [ ] AC009: JWTMiddleware 各种配置测试\n- [ ] AC010: Logger Middleware 测试\n- [ ] AC011: Metrics IncBackendRequests, RecordRequestDuration, IncErrors 测试\n- [ ] AC012: Valkey store 连接模拟客户端测试\n- [ ] AC013: StoreSandbox 有效和无效输入测试\n- [ ] AC014: GetSandboxBySessionID 存在/不存在会话测试\n- [ ] AC015: UpdateSandbox 测试\n- [ ] AC016: DeleteSandboxBySessionID 测试\n- [ ] AC017: ListExpiredSandboxes 测试\n- [ ] AC018: ListInactiveSandboxes 测试\n- [ ] AC019: UpdateSessionLastActivity 测试\n- [ ] AC020: Close 测试\n- [ ] AC021: Server 创建有效和无效配置测试\n- [ ] AC022: setWorkspace 测试\n- [ ] AC023: sanitizePath 各种路径输入测试\n- [ ] AC024: AuthManager LoadPublicKeyFromEnv, ValidateToken 测试\n- [ ] AC025: auth middleware 公共/受保护路径测试\n- [ ] AC026: ExecuteHandler 有效命令、超时、无效工作目录测试\n- [ ] AC027: UploadFileHandler, ListFilesHandler, DownloadFileHandler 测试\n- [ ] AC028: HealthCheckHandler 测试\n- [ ] AC029: LoadRSAPublicKey 测试\n- [ ] AC030: router, store, picod 包的现有测试保持通过\n\n---\n\n## 依赖\n\n- Go 1.21+\n- `testing` package (stdlib)\n- `github.com/stretchr/testify` - 断言和 mock\n- `github.com/golang/mock` 或 `go generate` - mock 生成\n- `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` - Valkey 客户端\n\n---\n\n## 测试模式\n\n### Mock 策略\n- 对依赖项使用接口 (Store, HTTP clients 等)\n- 使用 testify/mock 创建测试 mock\n- 对复杂模块使用 gomock 生成 mocks\n\n### 测试文件命名\n- 遵循 Go 约定: `*_test.go`\n- 与被测代码保持在同一包中\n- 使用 `package router` (不是 `package router_test`)\n\n### 表驱动测试\n- 对参数化场景使用表驱动测试\n- 示例模式:\n```go\ntests := []struct {\n    name    string\n    input   string\n    want    string\n    wantErr bool\n}{...}\n```\n\n### 测试覆盖率目标\n- Router 模块: 70%+ 代码覆盖率\n- Store 模块: 80%+ 代码覆盖率\n- Picod 模块: 70%+ 代码覆盖率\n\n---\n\n## 参考\n\n- Router 模块: `pkg/router/`\n- Store 模块: `pkg/store/`\n- Picod 模块: `pkg/picod/`\n- 通用类型: `pkg/common/types/`\n- 基础规范 (client-go): `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/store/store_valkey.go\">\nERROR [157:44] vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.expiryIndexKey).ZaddScoreMember undefined (type cmds.ZaddKey ha